 And then it got worse. The prime minister took a different route. 

00:07:18.640 --> 00:07:22.860
 For the people who are now confused about the geography of what we look at ... 

00:07:22.860 --> 00:07:24.200
 he did not go to Whitehall. 

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:27.080
 He drove under the arch of Foreign Affairs. 

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:29.380
 They follow a very strange route. 

00:07:29.380 --> 00:07:32.340
 They are going to the banks of the Thames, I would guess. 

00:07:32.340 --> 00:07:36.140
 They're going through the back entrance ... - I did not get any more points. 

00:07:36.140 --> 00:07:38.140
 I went back to parliament and discussed with Matt. 

00:07:38.620 --> 00:07:42.380
 You can get 10 extra points by doing something crazy at Sky News. 

00:07:42.380 --> 00:07:45.280
 Yes. - And I can still get 20 points ... 

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:48.240
 ... which would equalize the score. I think we're in the wrong place. 

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:52.120
 Yes. We can best go back there, I think? 

