 Then the prime minister went to explain the budget, and the camera crews outside had a break ... 

00:07:57.480 --> 00:08:01.420
 so we did the only thing we could do: look at it. 

00:08:01.420 --> 00:08:06.020
 The prime minister expects the economy to shrink by 3.5% that year. 

00:08:06.020 --> 00:08:08.360
 That is much worse than previously predicted. 

