 Politically, it might be interesting how David Cameron ... 

00:08:27.980 --> 00:08:30.400
 ... as I had predicted ... - Not fair! Not fair! 

00:08:30.740 --> 00:08:33.260
 It was a courageous attempt, but the security of Sky News ... 

00:08:33.260 --> 00:08:36.260
 managed to stop us soon. 

00:08:37.500 --> 00:08:40.640
 The problem is that Sky News has the cameras too high. 

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:42.980
 Way too high. - That's not going to work. 

00:08:42.980 --> 00:08:44.500
 We should climb. 

