 I'll come by later. 

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:03.840
 Sky News - wait a minute, this might well succeed. 

00:10:03.840 --> 00:10:05.840
 Okay, there we go, the bus is passing by. 

00:10:06.680 --> 00:10:08.680
 Ehm, from the left, right to the left. 

00:10:20.280 --> 00:10:23.140
 And to make it even more fun, the BBC was also live. 

00:10:29.420 --> 00:10:31.420
 That must have been successful. Yes! 

00:10:34.920 --> 00:10:38.680
 Time was running, and our deadline was close. 

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:42.140
 Matt had been stuck in traffic jams for hours. 

00:10:42.140 --> 00:10:46.120
 I was waiting in a queue, in the full sun. 

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:49.200
 A reporter forgot to say something. 

