 You can not see here that three policemen and two security people ... 

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:10.480
 were ready to arrest me if I was doing weird ... 

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:14.680
 ... so I could only salute to the camera. But it counted anyway. 

00:11:20.620 --> 00:11:25.080
 And it was time. We finally met at a parking lot on the south bank of the Thames. 

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:28.480
 Long day. - It was a very long day. 

00:11:30.400 --> 00:11:32.840
 You won, did not you? - I won. Sorry, Matt. 

